statements: SELECT id, user_id, scan_timestamp, location_id, fingerprint_data FROM FingerprintScanData;
SELECT scan_timestamp, user_id, location_id, id, fingerprint_data FROM FingerprintScanData;
SELECT user_id, location_id, id, fingerprint_data, scan_timestamp FROM FingerprintScanData;
SELECT location_id, fingerprint_data, id, user_id, scan_timestamp FROM FingerprintScanData;
SELECT id, fingerprint_data, scan_timestamp, user_id, location_id FROM FingerprintScanData;
SELECT id, fingerprint_data, scan_timestamp, user_id, location_id FROM FingerprintScanData WHERE user_id = 1
SELECT fingerprint_data, user_id, scan_timestamp, location_id FROM FingerprintScanData ORDER BY scan_timestamp DESC
SELECT * FROM FingerprintScanData WHERE location_id = 3 AND scan_timestamp > '2022-01-01'
SELECT id, user_id, location_id FROM FingerprintScanData WHERE location_id = 2 OR user_id = 3
SELECT id, fingerprint_data FROM FingerprintScanData WHERE location_id IN (1, 4)
SELECT * FROM fingerprint_scans;
SELECT id, fingerprint_data, scan_date FROM fingerprint_scans;
SELECT fingerprint_data, id, scan_date FROM fingerprint_scans ORDER BY scan_date DESC;
SELECT id, fingerprint_data, scan_date FROM fingerprint_scans WHERE scan_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT analysis_id, scan_id, analysis_result FROM scan_analysis ORDER BY analysis_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM fingerprint_scans WHERE id = 1;
SELECT fingerprint_data, scan_date FROM fingerprint_scans WHERE scan_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT AVG(id) AS avg_id FROM fingerprint_scans;
SELECT DISTINCT scan_id, analysis_result FROM scan_analysis WHERE analysis_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT fingerprint_data, analysis_result FROM fingerprint_scans JOIN scan_analysis ON fingerprint_scans.id = scan_analysis.scan_id;
SELECT * FROM fingerprint_scans;
SELECT scan_id, scan_data FROM fingerprint_scans WHERE scan_time > '2021-01-01';
SELECT DISTINCT anomaly_type FROM scan_anomalies;
SELECT scan_id, pattern_name FROM scan_patterns ORDER BY pattern_name ASC;
SELECT pattern_id, pattern_name, pattern_details FROM scan_patterns WHERE scan_id IN (1, 2, 3);
SELECT * FROM fingerprint_scans WHERE scan_time > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY scan_time DESC;
SELECT scan_id, pattern_name, pattern_details FROM fingerprint_scans s JOIN scan_patterns p ON s.scan_id = p.scan_id WHERE pattern_name LIKE 'Pattern%' ORDER BY scan_id ASC;
SELECT scan_id, anomaly_id, anomaly_type, anomaly_description FROM fingerprint_scans s JOIN scan_anomalies a ON s.scan_id = a.scan_id ORDER BY anomaly_id DESC;
SELECT s.scan_id, COUNT(a.anomaly_id) AS num_anomalies FROM fingerprint_scans s LEFT JOIN scan_anomalies a ON s.scan_id = a.scan_id GROUP BY s.scan_id;

SELECT s.scan_id, s.scan_time, COUNT(p.pattern_id) AS num_patterns FROM fingerprint_scans s LEFT JOIN scan_patterns p ON s.scan_id = p.scan_id GROUP BY s.scan_id, s.scan_time ORDER BY num_patterns DESC;
SELECT * FROM fingerprint_scans;
SELECT id, fingerprint_data, scan_time FROM fingerprint_scans ORDER BY scan_time DESC;
SELECT username FROM users WHERE last_login > '2022-01-01';
SELECT pattern_id, pattern_description FROM anomaly_patterns WHERE LENGTH(pattern_description) > 50;
SELECT anomaly_id, scan_id, pattern_id, detection_time FROM anomalies_detected ORDER BY detection_time ASC;
SELECT u.username, u.last_login, a.pattern_description FROM users u JOIN anomalies_detected ad ON u.user_id = ad.scan_id JOIN anomaly_patterns a ON ad.pattern_id = a.pattern_id
SELECT * FROM fingerprint_scans WHERE scan_time BETWEEN '2022-01-01 00:00:00' AND '2022-01-31 23:59:59'
SELECT u.username, COUNT(ad.anomaly_id) AS total_anomalies FROM users u LEFT JOIN anomalies_detected ad ON u.user_id = ad.scan_id GROUP BY u.username
SELECT a.pattern_description, COUNT(ad.anomaly_id) AS total_detected FROM anomaly_patterns a LEFT JOIN anomalies_detected ad ON a.pattern_id = ad.pattern_id GROUP BY a.pattern_id
SELECT u.username, a.pattern_description FROM users u CROSS JOIN anomaly_patterns a
SELECT * FROM fingerprint_scans WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT id, fingerprint_data, scan_date FROM fingerprint_scans WHERE id = 5;
SELECT pattern_name, identified_at FROM patterns ORDER BY identified_at DESC;
SELECT id, username, email FROM users WHERE full_name LIKE 'John%';
SELECT * FROM access_logs WHERE access_time BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31';

SELECT id, scan_date, user_id FROM fingerprint_scans WHERE scan_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT full_name, email FROM users WHERE username = 'john_doe';
SELECT anomaly_type, detected_at, details FROM anomalies ORDER BY detected_at DESC;
SELECT users.full_name, access_logs.access_time, access_logs.action FROM users JOIN access_logs ON users.id = access_logs.user_id;
